    <item>
      <title>Puppet-Gluster now available as RPM</title>
      <link>https://purpleidea.com/blog/2014/03/27/puppet-gluster-now-available-as-rpm/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2014 20:32:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://purpleidea.com/blog/2014/03/27/puppet-gluster-now-available-as-rpm/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve been afraid of &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RPM_Package_Manager&#34;&gt;RPM&lt;/a&gt; and package maintaining [1] for years, but thanks to &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.keithley.org/kaleb/kaleb.html&#34;&gt;Kaleb Keithley&lt;/a&gt;, I have finally made some RPM&amp;rsquo;s that weren&amp;rsquo;t generated from a &lt;a href=&#34;http://docs.python.org/3/distutils/builtdist.html&#34;&gt;high level tool&lt;/a&gt;. Now that I have the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/purpleidea/puppet-gluster/commit/241956937f9778c332335267fac1256792c71155&#34;&gt;boilerplate&lt;/a&gt; done, it&amp;rsquo;s a relatively painless process!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In case you don&amp;rsquo;t know &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/kalebkuechle&#34;&gt;kkeithley&lt;/a&gt;, he is a wizard [2] who happens to also be especially cool and hardworking. If you meet him, be sure to buy him a &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beer&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;$BEVERAGE&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &amp;lt;/plug&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;table style=&#34;text-align:center; width:80%; margin:0 auto;&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;wizard_penguin.png&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;size-large wp-image-799&#34; src=&#34;wizard_penguin.png&#34; alt=&#34;A photo of kkeithley after he (temporarily) transformed himself into a wizard penguin.&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;100%&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt; A photo of kkeithley after he (temporarily) transformed himself into a wizard penguin.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/br /&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/purpleidea/puppet-gluster/commit/241956937f9778c332335267fac1256792c71155&#34;&gt;The full source of my changes is available in git.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
